  - After changes, check producers, consumers, generated clients, server handlers, middleware adapters, and tests.
{{end}}
{{else}}
- No explicit contract paths were analyzed.
- Treat `api`, `proto`, `openapi`, `swagger`, `schema`, `types`, `sdk`, and `client` paths or filenames as contract changes.
- Contract changes usually affect at least one producer and one consumer; do not update only one side.
{{end}}

